  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK875">
<l>taṉṟuṇai yiṉṟāṟ pakaiyiraṇṭāṟ ṟāṉoruva</l>
<l>ṉiṉṟuṇaiyāk koḷkavaṟṟi ṉoṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who is alone and helpless while his foes are two should secure one of them as an agreeable help (to himself).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
